/span>[ως καὶ \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"ως\">ως\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[ἐπετέλε]σεν ἰδίοις \u003Cbr id=\"al7-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>συνμ]ύσταις \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou, Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κορνήλιος Μαγουλνι\n                    ανὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κορνήλιος\">[...].ΗΛΙΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μαγουλνι\n                    ανὸς\">ΜΑΓΟΥΛΝΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;ΑΝΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[.....]ΑΝΤΗΣ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἑκατης\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἑκατης\">ΕΚΑΤΗΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[...\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Κόρης\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κόρης\">..]ΡΗΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>ΑΓΟΣΟΣΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>[.....\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"ως\">ΩΣ\u003C/span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[.......]ΣΕΝΙΔΙΟΙΣ\u003Cbr id=\"al7-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">7\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>....]ΥΣΤΑΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003014_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022-07-14\" src=\"ISic003014_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003014.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022-07-14\" src=\"ISic003014-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003014_rear_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022-07-14\" src=\"ISic003014_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003014_rear.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2022-07-14\" src=\"ISic003014_rear-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on autopsy, combining suggestions of Manganaro and Robert (BE 1966)\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Robert proposed reading the prriestly title in line 3, and challenged various elements of Manganaro's original reading. The resolution of the second half remains far from certain. Manganaro originally dated the inscription to the first or second century CE, but in his final discussion (2011), without comment he redated it to the second century BCE. This seems deeply unlikely on the grounds both of palaeography and the use of a white marble plaque of this sort. At the same time, a cult inscription in Greek in the period of the Roman colonia is somewhat exceptional.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 34.0989 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> 1966.0525 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1965 177 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001452\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001452\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1977 160 dr \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Spigo 2005 77 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001569\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001569\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 2009 111 dr \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Fasolo 2013 57 no.2 fig.20 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002011\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002011\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>lunate letters (epsilon, sigma and uncial omega), somewhat crudely engraved amnd uneven / irregular in size.\u003C/p> Line 1-6  10-20  Line 7  10-11  Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[283,286,289,292,295,298,301,304],{"id":284,"html":285},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou, Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κορνήλιος Μαγουλνι\n                    ανὸς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κορνήλιος\">[Κορ]ν̣ήλιος\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μαγουλνι\n                    ανὸς\">Μαγουλνι-\u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)\u003C/span>ανὸς\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[ἱεροφ]άντης \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἑκατης\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἑκατης\">Ἑκατης\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[καὶ \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Κόρης\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κόρης\">Κό]ρης\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ἄγος ὁσί-\u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>[ως καὶ \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cspan data-text=\"ως\">ως\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[ἐπετέλε]σεν ἰδίοις \u003Cbr id=\"al7-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumb